{"type": "article", "id": 4710, "title": "200 卡路里的圣诞美食真的只有这么点？！", "description": "吃货慎入，但为了健康和身材，还是看看吧。", "date": "2014-12-25T13:59:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5567, "name": "Calorific"}, {"id": 1800, "name": "手机应用"}, {"id": 158, "name": "美食"}, {"id": 771, "name": "卡路里"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140829JMDezxrQdCt1El7U.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t节日总是和美食联系在一起。这两天，弥漫在空气中的烤火鸡、熏火腿、布丁、饼干以及甜红葡萄酒的香气是不是已经打开了你的味蕾？如果你想要任性地吃一顿圣诞大餐的话，那就只能坐等热量爆表了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t那些食品包装袋上的油脂含量与卡路里数字看上去没有那么吓人？这个名为「<a href=\"http://www.calorificapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Calorific</a>」的手机应用能将你摄入的卡路里全部视觉化，以 200 卡路里为计量单位，来看看你究竟超标了多少吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061408234RlbG1yABMTi5SVD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t硬币巧克力  35g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140823f1QXT5MDipqgsteZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t姜饼 56g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140824fLWh2btT8NezquQR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t圣诞布丁 61g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140824gu5IDvh40loEYyi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t烤鹧鸪  94g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140825YOSTFKkCWXgeD8qr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t肉馅饼 53g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061408257WDMhVeS06FwE5Bx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t糖汁胡萝卜  242g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140825aFno5PpsEhS4vc7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t小红莓果酱 125g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140826Z0cjFqxz4EiutYX6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t球生菜  690g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140826yXeUrBobaFx9lJVM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t加香料的热葡萄酒  183ml\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061408271EZt38wylJDhrkMg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t可口可乐  496ml\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140827ECRDlHuecdIkYhaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t鳄梨 125g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140827yoLF5K9bCQIJgSRZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t薯条 73g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140828KymBfa8bL0lX6Fk1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t黄油 28g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140828Kk6oJ8aTuShE31wF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t小辣椒 740g\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t当看到小小几枚硬币巧克力竟然与超过 1 斤的球生菜的卡路里含量一样，一小块黄油的卡路里含量等同于一盘堆成小山状的小辣椒时，面对“垃圾食品”和诱人的甜点，你是否会稍稍按捺住一颗吃货的心？\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;\">\r\n\tCalorific 手机应用将食物按照水果、蔬菜、糖果和零食、肉类&amp;鱼类、面包谷物类、牛奶&amp;乳制品以及饮料等进行分类，用户亦可以选择自行搜索自己食用的食物。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t目前，Calorific 支持<a href=\"http://www.calorificapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> iPhone 与 iPad</a> 免费下载，如若需要解锁全部食物，需另外付费。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t题图来自<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/art/200-calories-of-christmas-food-looks-like-this-12-24-2014/\" target=\"_blank\"> Designboom</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}